《'''入侵者'''》( 或稱寄居者 )( 英文 : Intruders)是一個由{{link-en|邁克爾·馬歇爾·史密斯|Michael Marshall Smith}}的小說 ''The Intruders'' (2007)改編。  2014年8月於美國有線電視網[[BBC美國台|BBC美國台]]首映。它是由[[BBC美國台|BBC美國台]]和[[BBC第二台|BBC第二台]]聯合拍攝。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Jeffery|first1=Morgan|title=Mira Sorvino on BBC Two's Intruders: "It's beautiful, but it is brutal"|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/interviews/a604702/mira-sorvino-on-bbc-twos-intruders-its-beautiful-but-it-is-brutal.html#~oTDaU4prsJAH3t|website=DigitalSpy|publisher=DigitalSpy|accessdate=24 October 2014|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925005330/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/interviews/a604702/mira-sorvino-on-bbc-twos-intruders-its-beautiful-but-it-is-brutal.html#~oTDaU4prsJAH3t|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="order">{{cite news|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|title=Mira Sorvino To Star In BBC America Series ‘Intruders’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/01/mira-sorvino-to-star-in-bbc-america-series-intruders/|accessdate=January 28, 2014|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=January 24, 2014|archive-date=2014-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612023105/http://www.deadline.com/2014/01/mira-sorvino-to-star-in-bbc-america-series-intruders/|dead-url=no}}</ref>  導演是{{link-en|愛德華多·桑切斯|Eduardo Sánchez (director)}}和{{link-en|丹尼爾·斯塔姆|Daniel Stamm}}。<ref>{{cite news|title=John Simm to star in BBC America drama Intruders|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25713249|accessdate=January 28, 2014|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=January 13, 2014|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129074759/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25713249|dead-url=no}}</ref>
